DataElement.preferredName: Laboratory Procedure Neutrophil Result Percentage Integer::0 Decimal Place Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The 0 decimal place numeric laboratory value measured, assigned or computed related to the assessment of the percentage of neutrophils in a specimen.
